{"about_the_game":"<strong>Power up and swing for the fences in this casual yet chaotic take on an American classic.</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Bad Hop Baseball is a game for one or two players<br></li><li> Two Player Hot-Seat PvP or One Player Against a CPU Opponent<br></li><li> Players take turns taking shots<br></li><li> Players control the power and timing of their swing. After that, it's up to chance!<br></li><li> Each shot generates a Baseball Outcome e.g. out / hit / double / triple / home run<br></li><li> As in baseball, when one side has been put out 3 times, that side is retired for the inning<br></li><li> When one player is retired, the other player will keep batting until they have been put out 3 times as well<br></li><li> The game is 3 innings long<br></li><li> Games cannot end it a tie! Extra innings will continue until a result is reached<br></li><li> In-Game, In-Session, and All-Time stats are saved! Because if there's one thing we baseball fans love, it's STATS.</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306340/extras/power_up_and.png?t=1676946568\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306340/extras/power_up_and_shoot_gif.gif?t=1676946568\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306340/extras/baseball_horizontal_2.png?t=1676946568\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306340/extras/lean_back_and_enjoy.png?t=1676946568\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306340/extras/hit_a_homer_gif.gif?t=1676946568\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306340/extras/baseball_horizontal_2.png?t=1676946568\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamst